    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "FlyJAL\nJH1FUQ\nTOKYO, JAPAN\nJAPAN\nAIR LINES\nOp.\n671\nOP. AKIRA FURUKAWA\nQTH. 3-3-118,\nHigashi, Shisui, Shisui-cho,\nInba-gun,\nChiba-ken,\nJAPAN",
      "MOUNT FUJI IS BEAUTIFUL FROM ANY PERSPECTIVE.\nUntil the age of airplanes, only the eagle had a view\nlike this. The Japanese love the trees, the rocks,\nand above all this inspiring mountain. With its\nskirt hidden by soft clouds, its snow-capped summit\nseems to float in the sky.\nPOST CARD\nRadio.\nDate\nTime\nUr Sigs\nBand\nRemarks\nGMT /JST\n'will be\nYour QSL\nis\nappreciated\nB*AE\nJAPAN AIR LINES\nJAL\nPRINTED IN JAPAN\n2015.166.0832."
    ],
